        'The knowledge model of skill says: learn the principles, understand the theory, acquire the information, then apply it. Study hard enough and performance will follow. This is how most formal education is structured. It\'s also how most online courses, most coaching programs, most self-help frameworks are designed. Read this, watch this, understand this — now you can do it.',
